                  </hi>. I am the son of the last witness. I saw what he has stated—he has told the story truly.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18390304-name-1069" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18390304-name-1069" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390304-name-1069" type="surname" value="JOBSON"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390304-name-1069" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE JOBSON</persName>
                  </hi>. My attention was drawn to this by my neighbour—I went after the prisoners, they were then standing, but the minute they saw us they ran off; we followed and took them—these are the shoes, there are five pairs, and they have my shop bill on them.</p>
               <p>(Herbert received a good character.)</p>
